"adj. 世界范围的 【考】 ecumenical : generality / entire : integrity(一般的有一般性/完 整的有完整性)反义词: diocesan(主教管区的 ) adj. 世界范围的; 一般的; 宇宙的 = universal; 全球基督教会的 【记】e出, cu苦, men人: 出来做苦人的是那些传教士, 目的是教全世界一般大众都接受他们的理念, 而那些呆在ocean的是diocesan(见下) 【类】ecumenical: generality = entire: integrity一般的有一般性 = 完整的有完整性 【反】diocesan(adj 主教管区的)来自ocean(海是易于传教的地方); factional(adj 派系的); provincial(adj 狭隘的) 【记】common ecumenical (adj.)  late 16c., ""representing the entire (Christian) world,"" formed in English as an ecclesiastical word, from Late Latin oecumenicus ""general, universal,"" from Greek oikoumenikos, from he oikoumene ge ""the inhabited world (as known to the ancient Greeks); the Greeks and their neighbors considered as developed human society,"" from oikoumenos, present passive participle of oikein ""inhabit,"" from oikos ""house, habitation"" (see villa)."
